{"tid":565074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十年前，GEM仲係叫大波GEM","createTime":"2018-02-18T15:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T16:23:40.000Z","uid":40525,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f44ffa08500f933469f52dc34f06ec65384e99b4","tid":565074,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"樂壇年年都有眾多新血加入，一同為廣東歌出一分力。2018年到了，有一班歌手入行十周年，當中不乏依然活躍於中、港、台的歌手，也有積極投身電視圈的演員，亦有人鮮於曝光和推出新曲。你又記得他們嗎？每每播放以下這幾首經典作品，都一定會令人記得這些歌手的音樂路。<br />\n<br />\n要數破最多紀錄的女歌手，非G.E.M.莫屬！當年她以唱作女新人的身份加入樂壇，出道作〈Where Did You Go〉的R&amp;B風格令人記住了她，亦因出色的現場演唱功力而被稱為「巨肺小天后」。G.E.M.的人氣居高不下，更以19歲之齡踏上紅館開演唱會，成為首個「最年輕於紅館開唱的歌手」。其後她赴內地參加節目《我是歌手》，由寂寂無名到整個大中華地區的人都知道她過人的創作和改編功力，多首翻唱作都成為大熱。現時更紅出國際，人氣如坐直昇機般「爆升」！<br />\n<br />\n想當年真係日J夜J呢條video <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vrGa75vT10U \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvrGa75vT10U%20&d=dX7SMwaj7NKPvTxtVBaW0AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ec8073dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vrGa75vT10U </a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2EMewIi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EMewIi&d=dX7SMwaj7NKPvTxtVBaW0AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6840ae93\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2EMewIi</a>"},{"pid":"6f263221dc12e26648f9915f8fa35fe1f6161998","tid":565074,"uid":9009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"大波大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfcd163cdcc2344f76128945ee453d3ce792b26","tid":565074,"uid":40525,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:00:59.000Z","msg":"一齊打個J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.n